News stories are also available on NewsLine Express, in addition to this, NewsLine Express is domestic radio as well as television networks to be set up soon in their agenda, NewsLine Express is with its unique feature of giving a editorial platform to its users is expects traffic of some 1 billion hits every week with an article submission with an approximate no of 1 million article submission every month from across the world.
